mp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=some%20gloves&amp;short_url=9YOn52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>一些手套的</u></a><a href="https://zdcs.link/zEj0N7?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=drywall%20patch%20kit&amp;short_url=zEj0N7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>石膏板补丁套件</u></a>。要进行维修，您将使用贴片覆盖受影响的区域，腻子刀以涂抹刺伤，以及砂纸或砂纸均匀地表面以准备油漆。这种维修需要30分钟到一个小时的工作时间，需要整整24小时才能治愈。此材料的价格仅为20美元，包括您需要的所有材料。</p><h2 id="clean-out-your-dryer-duct">清理干燥机管道</h2><p>清理干燥机的通风孔是您每年至少要做一次的琐事，而且即使是大多数新手Diyer可以解决的简单，也足够简单。您需要一个<a href="https://zdcs.link/98L30R?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=dryer%20vent%20cleaning%20kit&amp;short_url=98L30R&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>干燥机通风口清洁套件</u></a>或带有长喷嘴附件以及一些手套和<a href="https://zdcs.link/QPpMKo?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=screwdriver&amp;short_url=QPpMKo&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>螺丝刀</u></a>的<a href="https://zdcs.link/zJ2ZNl?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=shop%20vac&amp;short_url=zJ2ZNl&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>商店Vac</u></a> ，以使管道从干衣机中脱离。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Sealegend 37件干燥机通风口</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊的</span>$ 26.95</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$ 34.95</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省$ 8.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">现在购物</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/05NPS2KZLvXa3G0XPM7Z1gZ/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1742785883.jpg" alt="SeaLegend 37件式干燥机通风口清洁套件全向套件包括33feet Dryer通风口刷蓝色烘干机真空吸尘器棉布真空和烘干机适配器" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/05NPS2KZLvXa3G0XPM7Z1gZ/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1742785883.jpg" alt="SeaLegend 37件式干燥机通风口清洁套件全向套件包括33feet Dryer通风口刷蓝色烘干机真空吸尘器棉布真空和烘干机适配器" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">现在购物</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊的</span>$ 26.95</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$ 34.95</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省$ 8.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>您将使用螺丝刀卸下带有干燥机管道的软管夹，并带有带有家用真空吸尘器的干洗套件，或者用长喷嘴进行清洁套件，以清除管道内部的任何棉绒堆积物。该项目大约需要30分钟，只有35美元至55美元之间的费用。</p><h2 id="replace-a-broken-fence-board">更换折断的围栏板</h2><p>固定围栏板将使您有机会使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/avX7k8?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=drill&amp;short_url=avX7k8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>钻头</u></a>， <a href="https://zdcs.link/aM6DN6?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=tape%20measure&amp;short_url=aM6DN6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>胶带尺寸</u></a>， <a href="https://zdcs.link/91682A?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=chop%20saw&amp;short_url=91682A&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>切碎的锯</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/aewrDW?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=hand%20saw&amp;short_url=aewrDW&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>手锯</u></a>以及与<a href="https://zdcs.link/QL5lN0?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=fence%20board&amp;short_url=QL5lN0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>围栏板</u></a><a href="https://zdcs.link/aX2GOe?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=screws&amp;short_url=aX2GOe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>一起</u></a>进行练习。您将使用磁带尺寸来测量围栏板的高度，切碎的锯或手锯以将其切成长度，并钻孔以将新螺钉驱动到木板上以将其连接到栅栏上。该项目的价格在150到300美元之间，您需要的一切都取决于您是决定用锯还是切碎的锯。如果您只有一个木板要替换，则可能会换一个手锯，而切碎的锯将要简单得多。您可能可以在大约一个小时内完成该项目，包括测量和切割以及连接木板。</p><h2 id="regrade-the-gravel-on-a-walkway">在人行道上重塑砾石</h2><p>如果您有砾石路径，那么在某个时候，砾石将从脚步或天气中散布。为了改进您的路径并防止它侵蚀，您需要一些新鲜的<a href="https://zdcs.link/Qbx0DE?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=gravel&amp;short_url=Qbx0DE&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>砾石</u></a>， <a href="https://zdcs.link/QpXpkZ?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=piece%20of%20string&amp;short_url=QpXpkZ&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>一根绳子</u></a>，一<a href="https://zdcs.link/QKOnvG?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=pair%20of%20stakes&amp;short_url=QKOnvG&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>对木桩</u></a>， <a href="https://zdcs.link/aM6DN6?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=tape%20measure&amp;short_url=aM6DN6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>胶带尺寸</u></a>和<a href="https://zdcs.link/znXgDl?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=rake&amp;short_url=znXgDl&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>耙子</u></a>。您将使用砾石修补路径上的任何裸露斑点，并使用木桩，绳子和胶带尺寸沿路径均匀地铺开，以确保路径的中心在边缘上方一到两英寸处，以允许排水。该项目可能需要一个小时到一个下午的时间，具体取决于您的路径长时间。此材料的价格在30到100美元之间，具体取决于您需要多少砾石。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/best-diy-home-moprovement-projements-for-beginners？utm_medium = rss<dc:creator>贝卡·刘易斯</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Home & Garden]]></category></item><item><title>这款索尼无线游戏耳机目前处于最低价格</title><guid ispermalink="false">01JQ3GN02XNXNCK3DJAV56E45E</guid><pubDate> Mon, 24 Mar 2025 13:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description>耳机足够舒适，可以让您通过马拉松比赛，而不会疲劳。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01JQ3GN02XNXNCK3DJAV56E45E/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们可能会从此页面上的链接中获得佣金。出版后，交易定价和可用性可能会更改。</p><p>根据<a href="https://lifehacker.com/best-price-tracking-tools" target="_blank">Price Trackers</a>的说法， <a href="https://zdcs.link/9wXwb6?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Sony%20Inzone%20H9&amp;short_url=9wXwb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Sony Inzone H9</a>目前以198美元的价格出售，其正常价格为299.99美元，这是有史以来最低的。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Sony Inzone H9游戏耳机</div><