md:justify-start"> <span class="font-bold">$ 198.00<span class="font-medium">在亚马逊</span></span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$ 299.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省$ 101.99</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>凭借干净的黑白构建，RGB状态戒指和足够的角度才能匹配游戏机的氛围，该游戏耳机的设计是考虑到PS5用户的设计。头带的付出很大而不会太硬，并且其耳罩足够柔软，可以在没有耳朵疲劳的情况下进行马拉松课程。至于控件，在左耳柜上，您会发现一个永久连接的动臂麦克风（将其翻转时静音），以及ANC切换，音量轮和USB-C充电端口。在右边，您将获得力量，蓝牙配对以及平衡游戏和聊天音频的摇杆。这项<a href="https://This%20Sony%20Wireless%20Gaming%20Headset%20Is%20%24100%20Off%20Right%20Now%20%20The%20H9's%20headband%20has%20a%20nice%20amount%20of%20give%20without%20pressing%20too%20hard,%20and%20the%20earpads%20are%20soft%20enough%20for%20marathon%20sessions%20without%20ear%20fatigue.%20%20The%20Sony%20Inzone%20H9%20is%20currently%20on%20sale%20for%20%24198%E2%80%94that's%20%24100%20off%20its%20regular%20price%20of%20%24299.99%20and%20the%20lowest%20it%E2%80%99s%20ever%20been,%20according%20to%20price%20trackers.%20With%20a%20clean%20black-and-white%20build,%20RGB%20status%20rings,%20and%20enough%20angular%20flair%20to%20match%20the%20console%E2%80%99s%20vibe,%20this%20gaming%20headset%20is%20designed%20with%20PS5%20users%20in%20mind.%20The%20headband%20has%20a%20nice%20amount%20of%20give%20without%20pressing%20too%20hard,%20and%20its%20earpads%20are%20soft%20enough%20for%20marathon%20sessions%20without%20ear%20fatigue.%20As%20for%20the%20controls,%20on%20the%20left%20earcup,%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20a%20permanently%20attached%20boom%20mic%20(which%20mutes%20when%20you%20flip%20it%20up),%20along%20with%20the%20ANC%20toggle,%20volume%20wheel,%20and%20USB-C%20charging%20port.%20On%20the%20right,%20you%20get%20power,%20Bluetooth%20pairing,%20and%20a%20rocker%20for%20balancing%20game%20and%20chat%20audio.%20It%E2%80%99s%20simple%20to%20use%E2%80%94even%20mid-match,%20notes%20this%20PCMag%20review.%20Performance-wise,%20the%20Inzone%20H9%20brings%20active%20noise%20cancellation,%20decent%20bass,%20and%20surround%20sound%20simulation%20through%20Sony%E2%80%99s%20Inzone%20Hub%20on%20Windows.%20The%20ANC%20isn%E2%80%99t%20jaw-dropping,%20but%20it%20quiets%20low%20rumbles%20like%20fans%20or%20an%20air%20conditioner%20well%20enough.%20That%20said,%20high-pitched%20stuff%20still%20leaks%20in.%20The%20mic%20works%20fine%20for%20casual%20voice%20chat,%20but%20if%20you're%20planning%20to%20stream%20or%20record,%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20cut%20it%E2%80%94the%20voice%20quality%20feels%20more%20%E2%80%9CZoom%20call%E2%80%9D%20than%20%E2%80%9Cstudio-ready.%E2%80%9D%20Still,%20for%20gaming%20and%20Discord,%20it%20gets%20the%20job%20done.%20You%20can%20adjust%20sound%20profiles%20with%20the%2010-band%20EQ%20on%20PC%20and%20enable%20spatial%20audio,%20but%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20on%20PS5,%20that%20customization%E2%80%99s%20off%20the%20table.%20Sony's%20built-in%203D%20audio%20does%20kick%20in%20on%20console%20though,%20so%20you're%20not%20totally%20missing%20out.%20A%20relative%20downside%20is%20the%20complete%20lack%20of%20a%20wired%20connection.%20The%20H9%20operates%20solely%20over%20wireless%E2%80%94either%20via%20the%202.4GHz%20USB%20dongle%20or%20Bluetooth%E2%80%94so%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20manage%20battery%20life.%20Speaking%20of%20battery,%20Sony%20promises%20up%20to%2032%20hours%20per%20charge%20depending%20on%20how%20you%20use%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20bad,%20especially%20for%20a%20headset%20with%20ANC%20and%20Bluetooth%20running.%20You%20can%20pair%20it%20to%20your%20phone%20too,%20which%20adds%20flexibility.%20However,%20the%20Bluetooth%20audio%20quality%20won%E2%80%99t%20match%20the%20lower-latency,%20higher-quality%20signal%20from%20the%20dongle,%20especially%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20gaming.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20for%20booming,%20theater-like%20bass,%20this%20headset%20won%E2%80%99t%20blow%20you%20away%E2%80%94but%20it%20holds%20its%20own%20in%20the%20low%20end%20without%20distortion,%20even%20at%20higher%20volumes." target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开" rel="noopener">PCMAG评论</a>指出，它易于使用 - 甚至中期。</p><p>在性能方面， <a href="https://zdcs.link/9wXwb6?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Inzone%20H9&amp;short_url=9wXwb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">Inzone H9</a>通过窗户上的Sony的Inzone Hub带来了主动降噪，不错的低音和环绕声模拟。 ANC并不令人jaw目结舌，但它使诸如粉丝或空调之类的低声隆隆声非常好。也就是说，高音的东西仍然泄漏。麦克风可以进行随意的语音聊天，但是如果您打算流式传输或记录，它不会削减它 - 声音质量比“准备工作室准备”更“缩放呼叫”。尽管如此，对于游戏和不和谐，它可以完成工作。您可以使用PC上的10频段EQ调整声音配置文件，并启用空间音频，但是如果您在PS5上，则自定义不在桌子上。索尼的内置3D音频确实可以在控制台上启动，因此您并没有完全错过。相对缺点是完全缺乏有线连接。 H9仅在无线上运行（通过2.4GHz USB加密狗或蓝牙），因此您必须管理电池寿命。</p><p>说到电池，索尼承诺每次充电32小时，具体取决于您的使用方式。这还不错，尤其是对于ANC和蓝牙运行的耳机。您也可以将其配对与手机配对，从而增加了灵活性。但是，蓝牙音频质量与加密狗的较低延迟，较高的信号不符，尤其是在游戏时。如果您正在寻找蓬勃发展的剧院般的低音，那么这款耳机不会让您震惊，但是即使在较高的卷中，它也可以在低端没有失真。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/tech/sony-inzone-h9-wireless-gaming-headset-sale？utm_medium = rss<dc:creator> Pradershika Sharma</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Tech]]></category></item></channel></rss>